data.description: This spectacular 4 bed, 3 bath walk-out ranch in southwest Lincoln is just what you’ve been waiting for! Step inside the front door to a spacious living room with huge window and great natural light. The kitchen is just around the corner and opens to the dining room. There are three bedrooms down the hall. The primary bedroom features a large walk-in closet and 3/4 bathroom with updated lighting. There are two additional bedrooms and a full bath on the main floor. You are going to love the walk-out basement!! It is fully finished with a huge family room, 4th bedroom, 3/4 bathroom, laundry room AND a storage room! Enjoy the evenings on the East-facing deck and patio in the fully fenced backyard! It has a 2-car garage...with an extra parking slab in the driveway! You don't want to miss this one! Call for a showing today!
